title: GameHouse - Fairy Treasure - (Requested)[h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Fairy Treasure

Recover a historic treasure of jewels, fairy dust, and magic potions in 

this original brick-buster. Float the Fairy River from castle to cave 

in level after level of fast arcade fun. Use your magic raft to smash 

unique brick layouts, collect the storied treasure, and gather amazing 

power-ups. Featuring more than 120 challenging levels, an original 

story, and hours of brick-busting fun, Fairy Treasure is a thrilling 

trek through an astounding world. May the fairies be with you.
* Unlimited Play
* Over 120 Challenging Levels
* Unique Power-Ups
* Three Difficulty Settings
* Gorgeous Full-Screen Graphics
Windows 95, Windows ME, Windows 2000, Windows XP / 800 MHz / 96MB RAM / 

DirectX 5.0
